window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>What does a bunch of 20-somethings have in common? </p><p>1. A plan for how their lives will shape up in regards their careers, passions, dreams, love or sex. </p><p>2. A plan for completing the above plan. </p><p>Not if you are Vik or belong to his friend circle. Life here is anything but a plan. Here ideas for life are scoffed at, dreams never appear in their long slumber and having fun and being laidback is considered to be an 'in' thing. </p><p>Welcome to this world, where everything else is made to wait. </p><p>But will time wait for them? Or will they succeed in their farfetched dreams for which they haven't even started working? Oops...even thinking? </p><p>What role does Raghav, their best friend have in their life? Will he himself succeed in his unusual and rather unconventional idea of opening a dating club in the crowded, bustling Priya complex of Delhi? </p><p>Will time teach them a lesson? Or will they manage to cheat the calendar? </p>"; 
